<h3 id="doc-notes">Notes</h3>
<ul>
<li>Grayscale filters work on any element, but are most commonly used on
images and backgrounds.</li>
<li>For hover effects to be smooth, combine with
<code>.transition</code> and <code>.duration-*</code> utilities.</li>
</ul>
